README
	JHT, Febuary 7, 2022 : created

para is a subdirectory of LIBJ written in C++, which is aimed at implementing the features that help run hybrid OpenMP/OpenMPI programs.

OpenMP  : handles the parallelization within a node. 
OpenMPI : handles the parallelization between nodes

Each MPI task has a *unique* identifier in COMM_WORLD

COMM_WORLD is split into SHARED communicators. 

String Vectors:
These are specially implemented here as the Strvec struct. 
